mysql_groundtruth: SELECT DISTINCT PAGE_ID AS RECOMMENDED_PAGE FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN USER1_ID=1 THEN USER2_ID WHEN USER2_ID=1 THEN USER1_ID ELSE NULL END AS USER_ID FROM FRIENDSHIP) AS TB1 JOIN LIKES AS TB2 ON TB1.USER_ID=TB2.USER_ID WHERE PAGE_ID NOT IN (SELECT PAGE_ID FROM LIKES WHERE USER_ID=1)

SELECT DISTINCT l.page_id AS recommended_page FROM Likes l JOIN Friendship f ON (l.user_id = f.user2_id AND f.user1_id = 1) OR (l.user_id = f.user1_id AND f.user2_id = 1) WHERE l.page_id NOT IN(SELECT page_id FROM likes WHERE user_id = 1)
